&lt;/div&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/TheBusinessMakersRadioShow/~4/2snarruVa_8" height="1" width="1"/&gt;</description><feedburner:origLink>http://www.thebusinessmakers.com/special-features/austin-panel-webxtra.html</feedburner:origLink></item><item><title>The Overtime Show Business Scavenger Hunt!</title><link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/TheBusinessMakersRadioShow/~3/IwOQImpWxTY/ot-scavenger-hunt.html</link><pubDate>Thu, 29 Jul 2010 01:00:00 PDT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.thebusinessmakers.com/special-features/ot-scavenger-hunt.html</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The Interactive Strategies Conference 2010 has given the OT gals free range to give away a FREE pass to the IS Conference in whatever way we see fit. With that said, today we are launching a business scavenger hunt! Each week, you will get two questions. Keep track of the questions, and your answers. At the end of the hunt, send us your answers, and from those who submit, we'll choose a winner! Simple, easy, and FUN. And you know us, we're all about fun. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Each week we will add the latest questions but a little later after the BusinessMakers Overtime Show airs. To get a jump start listen to the show which airs every Wednesday at &lt;a href="http://www.thebusinessmakers.com/overtime"&gt; The BusinessMakers Overtime&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here we go!&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;1. What advice did the CEO of T3 (The Think Tank) give to aspiring women entrepreneurs?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;2. What does the CEO of Ground Force Building Systems see as the vision for the company in 5-10 years?&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class="feedflare"&gt;
